Did you know that about 1200 beneficial chemicals are released into the body just from practicing gratitude?

@drjoedispenza  joined me on The Doctor’s Farmacy to talk about the biology of gratitude, the significant changes it can have on your health, and so much more.

You can listen to the full episode titled, “How To Use The Power Of Your Mind For Spontaneous Healing,” on your favorite podcast app.
